\begin_layout Section*
4.20.
 Search is a fundamental ability
\end_layout

\begin_layout Subsection*
find function
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
find+search path+option+argument
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
Options are like : -user -group -ctime -type -size -name -perm.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
Could be used to search multiple locations
\end_layout

